  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates COU1 under an elevated Model Risk Level 3, reflecting increased model influence following removal of confirmatory bench testing from the regulatory submission. Thirteen credibility factors are addressed; three factors are recorded as not-assessed on the basis that their evaluation was considered beyond the scope of the current submission cycle.",
