      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must be a commercially validated CFD code with documented verification test suite and version control.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 was used; vendor-supplied verification and validation documentation confirms compliance with ASME V&V 10 software quality requirements at Gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
