      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) for the hemolysis index QoI must be below 5% on the fine mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the nominal pump geometry at 5 L/min, 3000 RPM. GCI for the normalised hemolysis index was 2.8% on the fine mesh (6.4 M cells), exceeding the acceptance threshold."
    },
