      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented review of simulation setup choices (boundary condition selection, turbulence model settings, hemolysis model constants) by an independent analyst.",
