    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Ten of thirteen credibility factors were assessed and all met or exceeded their required levels. The three unassessed factors (Numerical solver error, Use error, Equivalency of input parameters) were each characterised as beyond scope for the current submission. The overall credibility package is judged sufficient to support the regulatory decision under MRL 3, given the strong performance on the assessed factors and the conservative acceptance criterion (RH < 1) applied to the hemolysis QoI.",
